 
<p>
  *Spain and Portugal <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/environment/2022/jul/04/spain-and-portugal-suffering-driest-climate-for-1200-years-research-shows">suffering driest climate for 1,200 years</a>, research shows.*
  Scientists now know what causes this; it is directly connected with
  global heating.  As this gets worse, it will be a disaster for olive
  and grape production.

 